Enrolment Rate

Published; 2024

Here are the enrollment rates for Primary, Junior Secondary and Senior Secondary Schools in Nigeria
Primary School: The gross enrollment ratio in primary school in Nigeria in 2019 was 97.7%. The number of children enrolled in public
elementary school in Nigeria as of 2019 was 23,914,813. The number of children enrolled in private elementary school in Nigeria as
of 2019 was 4,750,327.
